headline.print_headline: Atletico Madrid Win La Liga Title After Draw at Barca
headline.main: Atletico Madrid Win La Liga Title After Draw at Barca

lead_paragraph: Atletico Madrid ended the decade-long dominance of Spanish giants Barcelona and Real Madrid by clinching a first La Liga title for 18 years in a thrilling climax to the campaign on Saturday.
